CatDescriptText: David Leo Lawrence was mayor of Pittsburgh from 1946 to 1959, and governor of Pennsylvania from 1959 to 1963.  He died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, speaking to two men, and woman wearing striped dress, gathered in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
